<script setup>
import { useStore } from "vuex";
import { onMounted, computed } from "vue";
const store = useStore();
const contacts = computed(() => {
  return store.state.property.contacts;
});
onMounted(async () => {
  await store.dispatch("triggerSetContacts");
  console.log(contacts);
});
</script>
